{"tid":2157743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"梁家傑、譚惠珠、曾國衞：We Connect","createTime":"2020-08-15T08:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T09:34:58.000Z","uid":339590,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f13d2804db604cdcbbee88728a636ac59a102c","tid":2157743,"uid":339590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"中共要有假民主粉飾太平，泛民率先舉腳贊成<br />\n<br />\n梁家傑：民主派應留守 譚惠珠：泛民應幫手解決問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543885-20200815.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543885-20200815.htm&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8c5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=4c56a498\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543885-20200815.htm&h=078fea16\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543885-20200815.htm</a><br />\n公民黨主席梁家傑認為，民主派議員有機會繼續留在議會，若果拒絕是很奇怪，否則政府可以「長驅直進、直搗黃龍」。<br />\n基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠認為，泛民立法會議員返回議會機會好高，期望如果他們返回議會，應幫手解決香港問題。<br />\n<br />\n曾國衞籲全體議員重回議會 又稱無計劃舉行補選<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543886-20200815.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543886-20200815.htm&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8c5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=4d0b8249\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543886-20200815.htm&h=5415b192\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543886-20200815.htm</a><br />\n政制及內地事務局局長曾國衞表示，人大常委會就第六屆立法會繼續履行職責不少於一年的決定，是最簡單及合情合理的安排，符合香港整體利益，他呼籲全體議員重回議會，不必有太多爭拗，齊心合力，對抗疫情。<br />\n至於議會現時仍有4個議席出缺，曾國衞表示"},{"pid":"830c845e8691b1fd267425803baaf0b37e01c42b","tid":2157743,"uid":271397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:44:50.000Z","msg":"梁家傑呢啲咪乖囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咩時勢呀而家&hellip;唔通仲添煩添亂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf929e036ec8d00183c3b2b2802dc23b70051a2","tid":2157743,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:34:58.000Z","msg":"你試下囉 , 我永久一票不投入過假議會嘅議員"}]}